    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nTyping `<C-\\><C-N>` in Ex mode crashes Nvim with `ext_cmdline` enabled (e.g: ui2).\n\nUBSAN:\n```\nneovim/src/nvim/ex_getln.c:3656:40: runtime error: null pointer passed as argument 1, which is declared to never be null\n/usr/include/string.h:408:33: note: nonnull attribute specified here\n    #0 0x000000d11366 in ui_ext_cmdline_block_append neovim/src/nvim/ex_getln.c:3656:33\n    #1 0x000000d0d257 in command_line_enter neovim/src/nvim/ex_getln.c:1015:7\n    #2 0x000000d077a2 in getcmdline neovim/src/nvim/ex_getln.c:2959:18\n    #3 0x000000d108bf in getexline neovim/src/nvim/ex_getln.c:3211:10\n    #4 0x000000c63dd5 in do_cmdline neovim/src/nvim/ex_docmd.c:599:47\n    #5 0x000000c60ab7 in do_exmode neovim/src/nvim/ex_docmd.c:296:5\n    #6 0x0000012ea4a2 in nv_g_cmd neovim/src/nvim/normal.c:5685:7\n    #7 0x0000012c2f84 in normal_execute neovim/src/nvim/normal.c:1250:3\n    #8 0x00000181b58c in state_enter neovim/src/nvim/state.c:100:26\n    #9 0x0000012a4405 in normal_enter neovim/src/nvim/normal.c:522:3\n    #10 0x000001007960 in main neovim/src/nvim/main.c:693:3\n    #11 0x7ff8372175b4 in __libc_start_call_main (/lib64/libc.so.6+0x35b4) (BuildId: ff0267465bc3d76e21003b3bc5598fd5ee63e261)\n    #12 0x7ff837217667 in __libc_start_main@GLIBC_2.2.5 (/lib64/libc.so.6+0x3667) (BuildId: ff0267465bc3d76e21003b3bc5598fd5ee63e261)\n    #13 0x000000401814 in _start (neovim/build/bin/nvim+0x401814) (BuildId: fc422df1cddccddf3742c27fa3ddbeab8b26a14d)\n\nSUMMARY: UndefinedBehaviorSanitizer: undefined-behavior neovim/src/nvim/ex_getln.c:3656:40\n```\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n```lua\nvim.ui_attach(vim.api.nvim_create_namespace\"lol\", {ext_cmdline=true}, function()end)\nvim.fn.feedkeys(vim.keycode[[gQ<C-\\><C-N>]], \"n\")\n```\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nNo crash. Shouldn't leave Ex mode either.\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\nNVIM v0.13.0-dev-171+gdf8d98173c\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nN/A\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nFedora 43 Workstation\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nghostty 1.3.1, tmux 3.5a\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\ntmux-256color\n\n### Installation\n\nSauce",
